branded gadhafi the real abductor of the newly freed hostages 
paul wilkinson director of the research institute for the study 
of conflict and terrorism said the hostage release proves an 
ongoing link between gadhafi and abu nidal 
the public should be warned against euphoria over the latest 
hostage release in lebanon wilkinson said in london it was 
obtained by a deal which violates the european community policy of 
no concessions under duress to terrorists or their sponsors 
a month ago france returned to libya three frenchmade mirage 
jet fighters that had been in france for repairs since 1986 libya 
pressing for delivery of the aircraft closed its ports to french 
ships in december 
