waddington on the hand three times waddington contends smith also 
spat on him and said now die you pig die from what i have 
smith denied biting the guard his attorney said the case was 
generated by aids hysteria and that scratches on the officers 
hands were caused by the jagged edges of smiths handcuffs 
if it wasnt for aids this man would never have been here 
