of reports alleging that a ring of physicians had performed 
unnecessary surgery on elderly patients for profit 
the jury found that the reports that the doctor had performed 
such surgery based on interviews with relatives of some of his 
patients were false as a whole and had ruined srivastavas 
reputation 
were elated the doctor with his wife and two children 
said after the verdict finally justice came through 
they saw the truth srivastava said of the jurors they 
saw all the evidence that was there and the facts convinced them 
in the series kenstv journalist ed gonzalez reported that 
srivastava had lost his privileges to practice at santa rosa 
