olympics in los angeles and launched with 31 shuttle flights the 
rock band van halens contract calls for a backstage stash of three 
pounds of mampms with all the brown and tan ones removed 
theres more to the modern mampm than shades of sienna however 
they come in red and white with hearts for valentines day green 
and red stamped with bells candles or trees for christmas and in 
pastel colors for easter 
the candy empire that produces all these varieties began in 1911 
with frank c mars small business in tacoma wash in 1940 his 
son forrest devised a candy modeled after a british confection a 
circle of chocolate covered with a crunchy coating 
mampms were born as much out of meteorological necessity as 
anything 
in those days the stores didnt have air conditioning the 
cars didnt have air conditioning the homes didnt have air 
conditioning mampmmars spokesman hans fiuczynski said 
the candy originally sold in paper tubes came in brown 
yellow orange red green and violet later replaced by tan 
although never patented each mampm beginning in 1950 was stamped 
with the trademark m to assure customers they were getting the 
real thing 
peanut mampms at first available only in brown were introduced 
in 1954 and colored peanut candies came along six years later 
it was during those years that mampm ltd settled in hackettstown 
a burgeoning rural community amid the hills and farms of 
northwestern new jersey 
since then mampms have survived not only the heat of summer but 
controversy and candycoated corporate challenges 
