agreed last week to reject the airlines latest reorganization 
proposal and seek the appointment of a trustee 
in formally filing its motion for a trustee tuesday the 
committee said easterns devastating constantly expanding and 
unending losses are extremely damaging to unsecured creditors 
the motion said eastern and texas air have been unable to 
project the results of easterns operations to the extent that 
the committee has lost confidence in their stewardship of the 
business 
