ago said she had known mccabe for years and approached him earlier 
this year about the possibilities of building a regional agency 
into a national agency 
i guess i piqued his interest she said 
beber silverstein handles 70 million in annual billings for a 
number of clients including humana health services florida power 
amp light first florida banks and floridagold orange juice 
the agency also claims credit for casting leona helmsley as 
the queen in ads for her helmsley hotels the agency was fired 
in 1987 mrs helmsley no longer appears in the ads she was 
convicted on tax evasion charges last year 
