offices and will be chairman of the new york office 
he is an extraordinary talent and im rooting for him said 
marvin sloves who founded scali mccabe with mccabe and remains 
with that agency 
mccabe said he hopes to help create on the great indepedent 
regional agencies in the country while having some fun and making 
some money 
