in the northeast and to problems with the former zayre stores the 
company has been unable to revitalize the stores by renaming them 
and has even lost some zayre customers by changing that chains 
advertising and pricing policies 
the zayre stores had been known for frequent promotions heavy 
advertising and discounted fashion items ames in contrast stocks 
more traditional merchandise and runs fewer promotions 
ames management is learning that it is very difficult to wean 
the customer from a promotional vendor said l wayne hood a 
